text: Against All Odds is the second studio album by English hip hop group N-Dubz. It was released on 13 November 2009 by All Around the World.Release date. Retrieved 2010-03-13. The album spawned the number one single "Number 1". == Track listing == ==References== Category:2009 albums Category:N-Dubz albums Category:Hip hop albums Category:Grime albums Category:R&B; albums
